00:20:43.610 --> 00:20:46.960
[Even if it might not fully suit your taste—]

00:20:47.400 --> 00:20:56.270
[Low-caffeine coffee, pure and gentle like Sooji.
Rich milk, sincere and honest like Sooji. Together,
they make a cool and stylish iced latte, just like Sooji.]

00:20:56.270 --> 00:20:58.330
[Even if it might not fully suit your taste—
Low-caffeine coffee, pure and gentle like Sooji.
Rich milk, sincere and honest like Sooji.]

00:20:58.330 --> 00:21:00.400
[Together, they make a cool and stylish iced latte, just like Sooji.
You worked hard today.
