00:21:07.510 --> 00:21:09.520
Actually, I'm not really a coffee person,

00:21:09.520 --> 00:21:10.790
but this cup here is amazing.

00:21:10.790 --> 00:21:11.510
Thank you.

00:21:11.590 --> 00:21:12.710
Thank you so much. She'll definitely love it.

00:21:12.710 --> 00:21:15.430
