00:21:20.300 --> 00:21:22.460
[Deeply impressed with himself]

00:21:22.840 --> 00:21:25.460
[If this doesn't move her, I'll get revenge!]

00:21:25.460 --> 00:21:26.940
Seriously, I'll get revenge. I will.

00:21:26.940 --> 00:21:28.280
[Sooji, wait just a bit]

00:21:28.280 --> 00:21:29.300
This is awesome.

00:21:30.030 --> 00:21:31.610
Come on. Let's go.

00:21:32.840 --> 00:21:34.590
