00:22:42.940 --> 00:22:43.700
[Beep]

00:22:43.980 --> 00:22:44.740
[Beep]

00:22:44.940 --> 00:22:45.660
[Beep]

00:22:45.890 --> 00:22:46.470
[Beep]

00:22:54.290 --> 00:22:56.240
[Startled]

00:23:01.900 --> 00:23:05.810
