00:23:12.920 --> 00:23:15.960
[Just consider it a pricey gesture for a Manito]

00:23:16.470 --> 00:23:18.040
[Please sign here.]

00:23:21.470 --> 00:23:22.930
[Oh, this is where I sign.] [Oh my.]

00:23:22.930 --> 00:23:24.850
[Oh my, oh my...]

00:23:25.350 --> 00:23:27.590
[Thank you.]

00:23:27.980 --> 00:23:30.140
[Hohoho, hello.]

