00:23:58.810 --> 00:24:04.180
[I've had the honor
of seeing you, Driver Park Saeyong.]

00:24:04.950 --> 00:24:10.350
[-Driver: The parody concert “Yellow Sea”
was about10 years ago, right?
-Well,]

