Look at me.

00:25:28.770 --> 00:25:31.470
[Why are all the drivers
I meet like this?]

00:25:31.760 --> 00:25:34.080
[I find it amazing. It's strange.]

00:25:34.150 --> 00:25:34.410
Thank you.

00:25:34.410 --> 00:25:36.610
