who is receiving the gift.]

00:25:43.000 --> 00:25:45.060
I'm the one who is receiving the gift.

00:25:46.950 --> 00:25:50.950
[A day filled with the joy of giving]

00:25:53.100 --> 00:25:55.510
[Lee Sooji: Thank you, sir.
Thanks to you, I arrived comfortably.]

00:25:55.510 --> 00:25:56.770
I was happy to meet you.

00:25:57.450 --> 00:25:59.920
[I heard it's going to snow on Saturday—
drive safely.]

00:25:59.920 --> 00:25:59.990
[-I'll remember this for a long, long time.]
[Touched]

00:25:59.990 --> 00:26:02.520
-I'll remember it for a long time. -Thank you.

00:26:03.090 --> 00:26:03.320
If you say things like that, I'll cry again. Please stop.

00:26:03.320 --> 00:26:05.130
[A driver who brought warmth
until the very end]

00:26:05.820 --> 00:26:06.820
Thank you.

00:26:07.750 --> 00:26:09.020
Thank you, sir.

