Saejoon was in that show.

00:29:10.440 --> 00:29:11.930
[A connection made through
the dating show Single's Inferno]

00:29:11.930 --> 00:29:15.040
-Him? -Yes, he's my friend.

00:29:15.600 --> 00:29:19.040
