[You actually came
in a sharp three-piece suit. Haha.]

00:29:19.540 --> 00:29:20.960
[What did you do before coming today?]

00:29:20.960 --> 00:29:21.150
-I was sleeping at home. -Sleeping at home.

00:29:21.150 --> 00:29:22.980
[Saejoon: I was sleeping at home.]

00:29:23.120 --> 00:29:23.660
Let's go.

00:29:23.660 --> 00:29:26.410
[You show up dressed like this
after just getting yourself together?]
