00:29:31.230 --> 00:29:32.830
-Sit down. -What is going on?

00:29:34.370 --> 00:29:35.390
What's my role?

00:29:35.390 --> 00:29:36.970
[Why did you call me here?]

00:29:37.280 --> 00:29:39.690
[Your role is...]

00:29:39.690 --> 00:29:42.350
