00:29:54.870 --> 00:29:56.410
[Dex: Excuse me, my gift… is it here?]

00:29:56.410 --> 00:29:56.650
[Here you are]

00:29:56.650 --> 00:29:57.680
-Yes. -Really?

00:29:58.740 --> 00:29:59.130
Thank you.

00:29:59.130 --> 00:30:01.930
[Finally holding the first gift!]

00:30:02.850 --> 00:30:04.680
[Ah. Hahaha!]

00:30:05.020 --> 00:30:07.060
[Returning with a huge smile]

00:30:08.220 --> 00:30:11.040
[To Bull. Fuel up on vitamins. Come on.]

00:30:11.040 --> 00:30:11.370
