01:10:36.890 --> 01:10:37.890
Oh, that's right.

01:10:37.940 --> 01:10:38.540
Gosh, you are Rabbit.

01:10:38.540 --> 01:10:39.770
[(Oh my, Jennie)]

01:10:39.770 --> 01:10:40.500
Jennie.
Hello.

01:10:40.500 --> 01:10:41.330
[Pretends this is the first encounter]
[Greets her shyly]

01:10:41.330 --> 01:10:42.180
Hello.

01:10:43.180 --> 01:10:43.500
I think there must be Jinyoung.

01:10:43.500 --> 01:10:46.980
[Only Jennie is kept in the dark?]
[Their real first encounter]

01:10:47.700 --> 01:10:48.740
[Peeping]

01:10:50.560 --> 01:10:51.660
I have to find it.

01:10:51.660 --> 01:10:53.100
[Turns around]

01:10:59.180 --> 01:10:59.720
[Just throwing the gift over]

01:10:59.720 --> 01:11:00.820
Who are you?

01:11:02.180 --> 01:11:03.210
[Identity unexposed somehow]
[An exhilarating first encounter]

01:11:03.210 --> 01:11:06.410
I just left it at the door,
and Jennie said, "Who are you?"

01:11:07.120 --> 01:11:07.180
What should I do?

01:11:07.180 --> 01:11:08.700
[Oblivious]
[Jennie appears a little shy on first encounter]

01:11:08.700 --> 01:11:10.350
It’s amazing.

01:11:10.430 --> 01:11:11.290
Me too.
Yeah.

01:11:11.380 --> 01:11:11.390
[A heart-to-heart feeling]
[Gosh, we finally meet (again)]

01:11:11.390 --> 01:11:12.420
Me too.

01:11:14.070 --> 01:11:14.710
Great.

01:11:14.820 --> 01:11:14.840
[Ah, right?]
[It's like looking in the mirror(?)]

01:11:14.840 --> 01:11:17.040
It's like looking in the mirror.
Right?

01:11:17.090 --> 01:11:17.840
Excuse me.

01:11:17.860 --> 01:11:17.940
[Where is the mirror?] [Where is it?]

01:11:17.940 --> 01:11:20.070
Where? Where's the mirror?
Excuse me.

01:11:20.080 --> 01:11:21.880
Where?
Excuse me.

01:11:22.110 --> 01:11:22.260
Where?

01:11:22.260 --> 01:11:23.060
[Oh!]

01:11:23.420 --> 01:11:24.210
[Noh Hongchul: Manito.
Jennie is your Manito!]

01:11:24.210 --> 01:11:25.060
Manito.
Why?

01:11:25.060 --> 01:11:26.640
[Noh Hongchul: Because she accepted everything.
She's happily playing along with you.]

01:11:26.640 --> 01:11:27.380
Really?
She's very cooperative.

01:11:27.380 --> 01:11:28.980
[Eh! Are you my Manito?]

01:11:29.510 --> 01:11:30.820
Are you my Manito?
Mr. Choo asked where the mirror was,

01:11:30.820 --> 01:11:30.980
and she played along with you.

01:11:30.980 --> 01:11:32.460
[Laughing at the same time!]

01:11:32.460 --> 01:11:33.180
Really?

01:11:33.180 --> 01:11:33.240
[Action!]

01:11:33.240 --> 01:11:34.460
Action.
What should I do?

01:11:34.460 --> 01:11:35.690
[Copy] [Paste]

01:11:35.690 --> 01:11:37.190
You guys are so in sync.

01:11:37.290 --> 01:11:37.380
Oh no.

01:11:37.380 --> 01:11:39.560
[A heartfelt interaction via the mirror]

01:11:39.560 --> 01:11:42.290
What should I do?
Looks like she must be my Manito.

01:11:42.420 --> 01:11:45.500
[Currently, the last Manito arrives]

01:11:47.540 --> 01:11:50.020
[Unlike during the day,
he's crisp and fresh now]

01:11:50.220 --> 01:11:50.910
So cute.

01:11:50.980 --> 01:11:51.000
[Knock, knock]

01:11:51.000 --> 01:11:52.460
I always wanted to see you.

01:11:52.490 --> 01:11:53.940
Me too.
Really?

01:11:54.780 --> 01:11:55.690
Let's talk later.

01:11:55.690 --> 01:11:56.980
Okay, I'll wait for you.
I really...

01:11:56.980 --> 01:11:58.020
[Knock, knock]

01:11:58.300 --> 01:11:59.420
[Lee Sooji: Oh! Someone is here.]

01:11:59.660 --> 01:12:01.180
[The last one! x2]

01:12:01.760 --> 01:12:02.540
[Finally, that's amazing] [My Manito]
Oh...

01:12:02.540 --> 01:12:03.050
Right?

01:12:06.470 --> 01:12:07.120
Hello.

01:12:07.750 --> 01:12:10.760
[Manito Member] [Dex arrives]

01:12:14.670 --> 01:12:17.520
[Pretending to be surprised]

01:12:17.710 --> 01:12:19.300
[Hello, bro!]

01:12:19.960 --> 01:12:21.340
Hello.

01:12:21.440 --> 01:12:22.280
Dex.

01:12:22.760 --> 01:12:22.840
[Dex: Nice to meet you for the first time, Jennie.]

01:12:22.840 --> 01:12:25.530
Hello.
Hello, Jennie. Nice to meet you for the first time.

01:12:25.530 --> 01:12:26.640
-It's Dex.
-Hello.

01:12:27.000 --> 01:12:27.340
Hello.

01:12:27.340 --> 01:12:29.770
[Noh Hongchul: (It's Dex) Say hi,
this is Rabbit.]

01:12:30.120 --> 01:12:31.840
[What Rabbit!]

01:12:32.140 --> 01:12:32.180
Rabbit!

01:12:32.180 --> 01:12:33.300
[Manito panics. What's going on?]

01:12:33.300 --> 01:12:33.970
Is this...

01:12:35.130 --> 01:12:36.440
[Dex: Confused.
Has my identity been exposed??]

01:12:36.670 --> 01:12:37.880
[Pretending not to know. Is he Rabbit?]

01:12:37.970 --> 01:12:38.070
[Hop hop]

01:12:38.070 --> 01:12:39.340
What Rabbit?

01:12:39.590 --> 01:12:40.090
[Are you Rabbit?]

01:12:40.090 --> 01:12:41.350
Why are you doing this?

01:12:41.470 --> 01:12:42.330
You're Rabbit.

01:12:42.470 --> 01:12:42.490
[First, all Manito members
have gathered]

01:12:42.490 --> 01:12:43.690
Let's sit down first.

01:12:43.850 --> 01:12:45.030
So it was Dex!

01:12:45.110 --> 01:12:46.570
So it was Dex.

01:12:46.690 --> 01:12:48.070
[Wait!!]

01:12:48.510 --> 01:12:51.010
[Dex: Assessing the situation.
How many identities have been revealed?]

01:12:51.360 --> 01:12:51.450
-Only one has been confirmed.
-Right now, just Rabbit.

01:12:51.450 --> 01:12:52.570
[Rabbit is confirmed (?)]

01:12:52.570 --> 01:12:53.320
Only one?

01:12:53.610 --> 01:12:55.210
No, how is it just one person?

01:12:55.550 --> 01:12:58.620
[It wasn't public,
but he confessed himself]

01:12:58.920 --> 01:13:00.730
[Talking nonsense.
Is this a cultural difference (?)]

01:13:01.100 --> 01:13:01.380
[Looking after him quietly -
he's very straightforward~]

01:13:01.380 --> 01:13:03.530
-Because he's very straightforward.
-He said he's Rabbit.

01:13:03.530 --> 01:13:05.420
[Noh Hongchul: And he said
he didn't bring gifts
(for Manitos) today.]

01:13:06.110 --> 01:13:07.310
-Is that so?
-Really?

01:13:07.560 --> 01:13:09.940
[That's his style~
He can... do that too?]

01:13:10.170 --> 01:13:11.680
[I didn't know that!]

01:13:11.680 --> 01:13:12.350
Really?

01:13:12.870 --> 01:13:13.930
You can give gifts.

01:13:14.030 --> 01:13:16.120
[You know what a Manito is, right?]

01:13:16.560 --> 01:13:19.660
[Whatever. It's a cultural difference (?)
I don't really understand what Manito is]

01:13:19.660 --> 01:13:20.170
-You don't understand what Manito is.
-I don't.

01:13:20.170 --> 01:13:21.300
[Those who know the truth
and those who suspect coexist...]

01:13:21.300 --> 01:13:22.250
As long as you learn it today.

01:13:22.250 --> 01:13:24.850
I really don't know anymore.
No idea who's who.

01:13:25.270 --> 01:13:27.840
[Choo Sunghoon: I said a lot
on the way just now.]

01:13:28.000 --> 01:13:29.130
[Choo Sunghoon: I even talked about Dex.]

01:13:29.330 --> 01:13:29.380
-Really?
-Really? Awesome.

01:13:29.380 --> 01:13:30.700
[Ah, really?]

01:13:30.920 --> 01:13:32.060
[While guessing (your Manito)?]

01:13:32.360 --> 01:13:33.570
[Choo Sunghoon: So I was surprised.]

01:13:33.840 --> 01:13:35.290
[Noh Hongchul: When did you think of Dex?]

01:13:35.550 --> 01:13:37.350
[Suddenly on guard. Why should I say it?]

01:13:37.610 --> 01:13:39.330
[First time panicking]

01:13:40.720 --> 01:13:41.380
[Oh~ mind games!
Oh~ you didn't fall for it]

01:13:41.380 --> 01:13:42.960
-You didn't fall for it.
-Mind games.

01:13:42.960 --> 01:13:43.590
You understood it a bit late, right?

01:13:43.590 --> 01:13:45.520
[Rabbit understood it a bit late]

01:13:45.520 --> 01:13:46.620
I only understand it now, a little.

01:13:46.620 --> 01:13:47.180
[Joined the info war late]

01:13:47.180 --> 01:13:49.610
It felt wrong.

01:13:49.840 --> 01:13:50.250
Now he wants to keep his secret.

01:13:50.250 --> 01:13:52.840
[Reasoning out Manito
with great satisfaction]

01:13:52.840 --> 01:13:53.970
So that's how it is.

01:13:54.270 --> 01:13:56.400
[Sooji's Manito is Jennie! Yes (?)]

01:13:56.400 --> 01:13:57.470
She gave me a gift.

01:13:57.470 --> 01:13:59.760
[She likes it
even when she's just breathing~]

01:13:59.760 --> 01:14:00.890
She loves it so much.

01:14:01.550 --> 01:14:02.470
That's true.

01:14:02.470 --> 01:14:03.020
[Confused]

01:14:03.020 --> 01:14:04.010
So happy.

01:14:04.280 --> 01:14:06.130
[Staring because I really like (Sooji)]

01:14:06.130 --> 01:14:06.800
Me too.

01:14:10.200 --> 01:14:13.280
[Mirror mode again]

01:14:13.390 --> 01:14:14.320
What should I do?

01:14:14.690 --> 01:14:14.850
I feel like I'm going to die.

01:14:14.850 --> 01:14:17.880
[Afraid of being found out.
Feels like I'm going to die...]

01:14:18.240 --> 01:14:20.210
[Lee Sooji: Well, then now
(while we're all gathered),

01:14:20.210 --> 01:14:23.610
[Lee Sooji: will be the time to learn
what our Manitos like, right?]

01:14:23.610 --> 01:14:24.110
Yes.

01:14:24.200 --> 01:14:25.320
-Yes.
-Yes.

01:14:25.320 --> 01:14:27.430
[Lee Sooji: I want to ask my Manito...]

01:14:27.870 --> 01:14:30.170
[Really? I'm very hungry right now!]

01:14:30.170 --> 01:14:30.810
Okay.

01:14:31.050 --> 01:14:31.370
[Are you listening, Fox?]

01:14:31.370 --> 01:14:31.980
Okay.

01:14:32.740 --> 01:14:33.150
Then...

01:14:33.150 --> 01:14:34.930
[Rummaging]

01:14:35.140 --> 01:14:35.560
[Manito?]

01:14:35.560 --> 01:14:36.280
Really?

01:14:37.360 --> 01:14:38.750
[Dex: I got this from my Manito.]

01:14:38.750 --> 01:14:40.360
Is this protein or something?

01:14:40.360 --> 01:14:40.630
[Vitamins?]

01:14:40.630 --> 01:14:41.670
-Vitamins.
-My Manito...

01:14:41.670 --> 01:14:41.860
-My Manito gave me this.
-A gift.

01:14:41.860 --> 01:14:43.140
[Openly revealing Manito's gift]

01:14:43.140 --> 01:14:43.780
Really?

01:14:43.810 --> 01:14:44.390
Yes.

01:14:44.390 --> 01:14:46.280
[Staring at it uneasily]

01:14:46.280 --> 01:14:46.780
Vitamins.

01:14:46.780 --> 01:14:47.810
-Vitamins.
-My Manito...

01:14:47.810 --> 01:14:48.700
[Huh... oh... ha...]

01:14:48.700 --> 01:14:50.650
-My Manito gave me this.
-A gift.

01:14:50.780 --> 01:14:51.430
Yes.

01:14:51.550 --> 01:14:52.130
-A gift.
-Yes.

01:14:52.130 --> 01:14:52.190
[Glances]

01:14:52.190 --> 01:14:52.810
Really?

01:14:53.640 --> 01:14:53.750
-Jennie.
-Eat this.

01:14:53.750 --> 01:14:55.630
[Jennie. Haha. Why are you so surprised?]

01:14:56.130 --> 01:14:56.690
-Jennie.
-Eat this.

01:14:56.690 --> 01:14:57.350
[Haa... haa...]

01:14:57.350 --> 01:14:58.550
Why are you so surprised?

01:14:58.550 --> 01:14:59.570
Is it from you?

01:14:59.570 --> 01:15:02.050
[Is it Jennie? Surprised because
it (the gift) was passed on?]

01:15:02.050 --> 01:15:02.980
-Jennie.
-What?

01:15:03.110 --> 01:15:03.420
-Please don't focus on me so much.
-Why?

01:15:03.420 --> 01:15:06.380
[Please don't focus on me so much...]

01:15:06.910 --> 01:15:08.320
If we talk more,
we might figure something out.

01:15:08.320 --> 01:15:09.900
[I really...!]

01:15:10.070 --> 01:15:12.310
[Feels like my heart
is about to jump out of my body]

01:15:12.510 --> 01:15:12.720
Me too.

01:15:12.720 --> 01:15:13.600
[Dex is also confused]

01:15:13.600 --> 01:15:15.310
I need to calm down first.

01:15:15.510 --> 01:15:18.200
[Haa... haa...]

01:15:18.740 --> 01:15:19.100
Save me.

01:15:19.100 --> 01:15:20.230
[Only more chaos
as the night deepens at HQ]

01:15:20.230 --> 01:15:23.230
Since we're all gathered,
let's eat something first.

01:15:23.230 --> 01:15:23.980
Have some tea.

01:15:23.980 --> 01:15:25.830
[Snack time for starving Sooji]

01:15:25.830 --> 01:15:26.780
Have some tea.

01:15:27.020 --> 01:15:29.190
[I'm really your fan!]

01:15:29.190 --> 01:15:29.420
-Me too.
-No, I'm really your fan.

01:15:29.420 --> 01:15:32.310
[Shy confession of fandom]

01:15:33.490 --> 01:15:36.120
[Jennie: I wondered when we'd meet.
This is amazing!]

01:15:36.530 --> 01:15:38.120
[Thank you...]

01:15:38.470 --> 01:15:40.140
[Lee Sooji: You recognizing me
is already an honor.]

01:15:40.140 --> 01:15:41.780
-I really...
-It's already an honor.

01:15:41.780 --> 01:15:42.820
[Really? Thank you... I love you!
I've seen everything]

01:15:42.820 --> 01:15:45.480
-Really? Thank you.
-I really seen everything.

01:15:45.520 --> 01:15:46.140
-Really?
-You're really the best.

01:15:46.140 --> 01:15:47.120
[Really the best!]

01:15:47.120 --> 01:15:48.850
-I'm really...
-Really great.

01:15:49.220 --> 01:15:49.580
Number one.

01:15:49.580 --> 01:15:50.300
[In front of her fan,
Sooji turns into a shy girl too…]

01:15:50.300 --> 01:15:51.500
-Thank you.
-Really.

01:15:51.550 --> 01:15:53.150
-No, you're number one.
-No.

01:15:53.400 --> 01:15:53.480
You're the queen.

01:15:53.480 --> 01:15:54.860
[Meeting fans (?) brings inner peace]

01:15:54.860 --> 01:15:56.690
I really like you.

01:15:56.710 --> 01:15:58.390
[Start~ Us!]

01:16:00.310 --> 01:16:01.040
What is that?

01:16:01.610 --> 01:16:02.450
What is that?

01:16:03.420 --> 01:16:04.190
What is that?

01:16:04.280 --> 01:16:04.470
-We are mirrors.
-We are mirrors.

01:16:04.470 --> 01:16:05.470
[Addicted. We're mirrors!]

01:16:05.470 --> 01:16:06.110
Mirrors.

01:16:06.190 --> 01:16:07.240
-Yes.
-Yes.

01:16:11.570 --> 01:16:14.730
[Arriving with many gifts for the Manitos]

01:16:15.180 --> 01:16:18.160
[A familiar man in a three-piece suit]

01:16:18.600 --> 01:16:18.640
[The room is buzzing with talk]

01:16:18.640 --> 01:16:19.960
I heard about this.

01:16:20.220 --> 01:16:21.440
I thought, me too. Thought about it a bit.

01:16:21.440 --> 01:16:22.830
[Knock knock!]

01:16:22.830 --> 01:16:24.500
That massage earlier,

01:16:25.560 --> 01:16:27.360
they even mentioned a playlist.

01:16:29.130 --> 01:16:32.250
[Politely entering quietly]

01:16:32.510 --> 01:16:32.650
[Whoosh~]

01:16:32.650 --> 01:16:35.120
I don't have much desire for food.

01:16:35.240 --> 01:16:36.570
But if we live together,

01:16:36.790 --> 01:16:37.300
[Blank stare...]

01:16:37.300 --> 01:16:38.480
we'll cook for each other, right?

01:16:38.480 --> 01:16:39.010
Yeah.

01:16:39.300 --> 01:16:40.780
[Looks like someone is coming in?]

01:16:44.460 --> 01:16:44.610
-Hello.
-Hello.

01:16:44.610 --> 01:16:45.820
[Huh]

01:16:46.830 --> 01:16:48.210
-Hello.
-Hello.

01:16:48.600 --> 01:16:48.850
What?

01:16:48.850 --> 01:16:52.890
[Confused by the ill-timed
catfish man]

01:16:53.790 --> 01:16:55.310
[He's here, three-piece suit!]

01:16:55.310 --> 01:16:55.950
Hello.

01:16:56.860 --> 01:16:59.170
[DE avatar on a mission, Saejoon]

01:16:59.170 --> 01:17:00.090
Hello.

01:17:00.640 --> 01:17:02.380
[A gentleman...]

01:17:02.960 --> 01:17:04.890
[Gave this to you...]

01:17:06.550 --> 01:17:10.090
[A gentleman what?]

01:17:10.390 --> 01:17:10.980
2, 3. The gentleman over there.

01:17:10.980 --> 01:17:13.260
[Dex inputs]

01:17:13.260 --> 01:17:14.440
This is for you.

01:17:14.540 --> 01:17:14.740
A gentleman...

01:17:14.740 --> 01:17:16.740
[DE avatar outputs]

01:17:16.740 --> 01:17:17.740
gave this to you.

01:17:18.350 --> 01:17:18.690
[Seeing it in person is pretty cringey]

01:17:18.690 --> 01:17:19.830
A gentleman...

01:17:21.000 --> 01:17:22.050
Looks like there's real gear.

01:17:22.050 --> 01:17:23.840
[Bows. I'm leaving...]

01:17:24.430 --> 01:17:25.560
I'll get going then.

01:17:27.040 --> 01:17:27.690
2, 3.

01:17:27.690 --> 01:17:30.140
[Excessive politeness is part of the plan]

01:17:30.140 --> 01:17:31.270
I'll get going then.

01:17:32.440 --> 01:17:32.720
[Whoa!! Oh...!]

01:17:32.720 --> 01:17:33.690
What is this?

01:17:34.780 --> 01:17:35.480
Amazing!

01:17:36.810 --> 01:17:37.190
What is this?

01:17:37.190 --> 01:17:38.340
[Going crazy because it's too gentlemanly]

01:17:38.340 --> 01:17:39.190
What's that?

01:17:40.050 --> 01:17:40.910
I'll get going.

01:17:41.370 --> 01:17:42.100
What is this?

01:17:42.850 --> 01:17:44.010
-Amazing.
-What was that?

01:17:44.010 --> 01:17:44.420
[Happy to get a gift but somehow annoyed]

01:17:44.420 --> 01:17:45.380
-What?
-What was that?

01:17:45.380 --> 01:17:46.110
What is this?

01:17:46.370 --> 01:17:46.960
-Where are you going?
-What?

01:17:46.960 --> 01:17:48.650
[Where are you going~~~!]

01:17:49.100 --> 01:17:49.920
Does he have a phobia of shows too?

01:17:49.920 --> 01:17:50.610
[(Runs off)]

01:17:50.610 --> 01:17:51.790
Or that's all he's meant to say?

01:17:51.790 --> 01:17:52.190
-He ran away!
-Where are you going?

01:17:52.190 --> 01:17:53.430
[Where are you going!]

01:17:53.790 --> 01:17:56.670
[Going back to my house...]

01:17:56.760 --> 01:17:56.970
-He ran away!
-Where are you going?

01:17:56.970 --> 01:17:58.070
[Ran away!]

01:17:58.100 --> 01:18:00.020
[Denying. No, no, not my friend.
Is he your friend?]

01:18:00.220 --> 01:18:00.330
-What's going on?
-He brought a gift for Rabbit?

01:18:00.330 --> 01:18:02.350
[Noh Hongchul: He brought
a gift for Rabbit?]

01:18:02.540 --> 01:18:03.620
[I got a gift]

01:18:03.620 --> 01:18:04.280
What is it? Do you like it?

01:18:04.280 --> 01:18:04.760
[Jennie: What's inside
(the shopping bag)?]

01:18:04.760 --> 01:18:06.090
-What's inside?
-Wait.

01:18:06.550 --> 01:18:06.650
[Choo Sunghoon: Is it a gift
from one of you?]

