01:25:59.230 --> 01:25:59.400
-This really is good training.
-Seriously.

01:25:59.400 --> 01:26:01.260
[This is really a good training(?)]

01:26:01.580 --> 01:26:03.390
[Next time we can do better
as Secret Manitos]

01:26:03.690 --> 01:26:03.800
-We can do better.
-Really.

01:26:03.800 --> 01:26:04.730
[After a “perfect rehearsal,”
they've realized]

01:26:04.730 --> 01:26:05.900
Having practiced like this once,

01:26:05.900 --> 01:26:07.030
[Perfectly!]

01:26:07.030 --> 01:26:08.000
we really can do it perfectly next time.

01:26:08.000 --> 01:26:08.970
[The only regret belongs to Rabbit
who made all the plans…]

01:26:08.970 --> 01:26:10.030
I think I get it now.

01:26:11.640 --> 01:26:13.770
[Jennie: Can I show this?]

01:26:14.160 --> 01:26:14.750
You said earlier you wanted to do this.

01:26:14.750 --> 01:26:15.500
[Turns out Jennie found Jinyoung…!]

01:26:15.500 --> 01:26:17.160
-I'm honestly so touched.
-I really worked hard to find him.

01:26:17.160 --> 01:26:18.420
This is crazy.

01:26:18.800 --> 01:26:21.020
[Jinyoung: So moved]

01:26:21.180 --> 01:26:22.460
When I saw it, I felt really touched too.

01:26:22.460 --> 01:26:24.570
[Sunghoon lost in thought for a moment]

01:26:24.570 --> 01:26:27.620
-Really.
-It wasn't even that much, just about this many.

01:26:27.620 --> 01:26:28.630
Searching through all these…

01:26:28.630 --> 01:26:29.730
It was such a beautiful time.

01:26:29.730 --> 01:26:30.930
[So what are you doing tomorrow?]

01:26:31.050 --> 01:26:33.790
[I was planning
to receive gifts tomorrow]

01:26:34.090 --> 01:26:35.560
[A loud inner monologue everyone can hear]

01:26:35.560 --> 01:26:36.290
[It's all over my mind]

01:26:36.290 --> 01:26:37.030
[Openly craving kindness]

01:26:37.670 --> 01:26:39.560
-That was my plan.
-As expected of you.

01:26:39.560 --> 01:26:41.110
[Hyung, what are you doing (tomorrow)?]

01:26:41.530 --> 01:26:43.590
[I was planning to give gifts]

01:26:43.590 --> 01:26:44.050
Really?

01:26:44.150 --> 01:26:45.870
[Oh, then that's perfect!]

01:26:46.770 --> 01:26:47.520
So…

01:26:48.550 --> 01:26:51.580
[Let's meet during the day tomorrow!
So sudden?]

01:26:51.580 --> 01:26:53.320
Meet me tomorrow, in the daytime.

01:26:53.320 --> 01:26:54.390
[Got it!
You don't have any schedule, right?]

01:26:54.390 --> 01:26:55.340
I got it, yeah.

01:26:55.420 --> 01:26:56.520
You've got ideas.

01:26:56.520 --> 01:26:58.160
[I got it]

01:26:58.940 --> 01:27:02.140
[The YouTube thing on the 15th (tomorrow)…]

01:27:03.140 --> 01:27:03.160
Just change the date. Help me adjust it.

01:27:03.160 --> 01:27:06.770
[Rushing to rearrange
the schedule because of Hongchul]

01:27:06.980 --> 01:27:09.350
[I've thought about it a lot. How about…]

01:27:09.940 --> 01:27:16.080
[You and I go to
Japan tomorrow right away.]

01:27:16.940 --> 01:27:17.120
What? What is this?

01:27:17.120 --> 01:27:20.210
[Is this for real?? Sudden development
after the Manito mission ended]

01:27:20.210 --> 01:27:21.250
[Is this for real? Or is he joking?
Or did I misunderstand?]

01:27:21.250 --> 01:27:22.380
Did I get this wrong?

01:27:22.520 --> 01:27:24.320
[You are a Travel YouTuber
now, aren't you?]

01:27:24.710 --> 01:27:26.150
[Noh Hongchul:
I'm not a Travel YouTuber, hahaha]

01:27:26.150 --> 01:27:28.540
[Noh Hongchul: I just travel a lot]

01:27:28.650 --> 01:27:29.600
[Looks like we're really going!]

01:27:29.600 --> 01:27:30.620
Let's go together—you and I.

01:27:30.620 --> 01:27:32.720
[Choo Sunghoon: We'll go to Japan
and I'll film YouTube with you]

01:27:34.320 --> 01:27:34.660
That was actually part of my plan.

01:27:34.660 --> 01:27:35.890
[Japan trip originally planned]

01:27:35.890 --> 01:27:36.500
I already told them.

01:27:36.500 --> 01:27:38.350
(guest appearance on
Hongchul's YouTube channel)]

01:27:38.800 --> 01:27:41.230
[Go to Japan,
eat good food, and come back.]

01:27:41.460 --> 01:27:43.170
[That will be my gift]

01:27:43.170 --> 01:27:44.100
What should I do?

01:27:44.480 --> 01:27:46.210
[Ohhh~~~ so thoughtful~~]

01:27:46.210 --> 01:27:48.160
-So thoughtful!
-Not really.

01:27:48.160 --> 01:27:48.260
[Rabbit's bold drive]

01:27:48.260 --> 01:27:49.990
-Really!
-Not really!

01:27:50.050 --> 01:27:51.270
-I'll go along with you.
-Not really!

01:27:51.270 --> 01:27:53.990
[Wow, men's friendship is so cool]

01:27:54.190 --> 01:27:54.680
Let's do something fun together.

01:27:54.680 --> 01:27:55.870
[What should I do…]

01:27:55.870 --> 01:27:57.300
And it's Japan, after all.

01:27:57.300 --> 01:27:57.310
This feels like a real present.

01:27:57.310 --> 01:27:59.950
[I've been thinking all day
about a gift with a special experience.]

01:28:00.540 --> 01:28:02.390
[You go travel together, seriously…]

01:28:02.520 --> 01:28:03.260
It's a must. A must.

01:28:03.260 --> 01:28:03.940
[No need to say more—absolutely!
I'll just follow Rabbit]

01:28:03.940 --> 01:28:05.090
-So cool.
-So cool.

01:28:05.150 --> 01:28:06.710
Unbelievable.

01:28:07.140 --> 01:28:08.830
[Then make a group chat]

01:28:08.930 --> 01:28:09.500
-I will.
-Okay.

01:28:09.500 --> 01:28:10.290
[An impromptu friendship trip
decided on the spot (?)]

01:28:10.290 --> 01:28:11.420
Good job.

01:28:12.470 --> 01:28:15.800
[But… there should be tickets, right…?]

01:28:15.890 --> 01:28:16.520
[Sunghoon × Hongchul – heading to Japan!]

01:28:16.520 --> 01:28:17.460
Let's leave now!

01:28:17.540 --> 01:28:18.490
-Let's go.
-OK!

01:28:18.670 --> 01:28:19.080
[Excited Hongchul]

01:28:19.080 --> 01:28:20.360
Honestly, I'm really excited.

01:28:20.360 --> 01:28:21.560
I love Japanese ice cream.

01:28:21.560 --> 01:28:21.590
Then let's go to Hokkaido!

01:28:21.590 --> 01:28:23.030
[Big brother with max improvisation power]

01:28:23.030 --> 01:28:24.970
We should check flights.

01:28:24.970 --> 01:28:26.520
[Any tickets?]

01:28:26.760 --> 01:28:27.570
[Sold out]

01:28:27.570 --> 01:28:28.400
[No tickets]

01:28:28.400 --> 01:28:28.500
Let's change destinations.

01:28:28.500 --> 01:28:29.700
[Then let's go somewhere else]

01:28:29.700 --> 01:28:30.900
How about Fukuoka?
[Let's go to Fukuoka?]

01:28:30.900 --> 01:28:31.090
[(Nope) Let's go to Osaka.]

01:28:31.090 --> 01:28:32.080
Let's go to Osaka, Osaka.

01:28:32.080 --> 01:28:33.260
[(This sudden…?)]

01:28:33.300 --> 01:28:34.680
[I've met someone even crazier than me]

01:28:34.760 --> 01:28:37.370
[Improvisation beyond imagination.
Here, here, here!]

01:28:37.420 --> 01:28:39.020
[Feels like we've ridden
every transport possible…]

01:28:39.230 --> 01:28:40.440
[12 hours away from home—how does
the first grateful meal taste…?!]

01:28:40.440 --> 01:28:42.150
Even if someone cooks the same way,
they can't recreate this flavor.

01:28:42.150 --> 01:28:43.790
Never. Absolutely impossible.

01:28:43.790 --> 01:28:43.900
[And also]

01:28:43.900 --> 01:28:44.860
It's black!

01:28:44.860 --> 01:28:44.960
[Finally starting]

01:28:44.960 --> 01:28:45.660
So cool.

01:28:45.720 --> 01:28:45.810
-Let's go!
-Let's go!

01:28:45.810 --> 01:28:47.750
[Secret Manito Big Mission]

01:28:47.790 --> 01:28:48.680
[HQ Staff: The ones
who will become your]

01:28:48.680 --> 01:28:50.020
[HQ Staff: Secret Manitos]

01:28:50.240 --> 01:28:51.720
[Are elementary school students]

01:28:51.720 --> 01:28:52.630
Really?

01:28:52.820 --> 01:28:52.870
[106 students in the entire school]

01:28:52.870 --> 01:28:54.270
That's the whole school?

01:28:54.450 --> 01:28:54.630
[106 students – for one very special day]

01:28:54.630 --> 01:28:55.360
A wish tree?

01:28:55.780 --> 01:28:56.640
We need to look carefully.

01:28:56.640 --> 01:28:57.470
[Got the cute and tiny preferences]

01:28:57.470 --> 01:28:59.020
So adorable.

01:28:59.120 --> 01:29:00.330
Let me live happily.

01:29:00.400 --> 01:29:01.900
[I really don't know
how to respond to this…]

01:29:01.900 --> 01:29:04.850
[How about doing nothing for them
and teaching them what reality is?]

01:29:04.860 --> 01:29:05.030
[Stock investment tips…]

01:29:05.030 --> 01:29:06.530
Let's tell them stock news.

01:29:06.530 --> 01:29:07.230
[Members who lost direction]

01:29:07.230 --> 01:29:08.420
These people, seriously…

01:29:08.420 --> 01:29:08.440
Let's split up first.

01:29:08.440 --> 01:29:09.530
[Split up!]

01:29:09.530 --> 01:29:09.600
[Officially entering gift strategy mode]

01:29:09.600 --> 01:29:10.160
Let's go!

01:29:10.500 --> 01:29:11.410
Let's go!

01:29:11.450 --> 01:29:11.500
[For Ji-an!
Not leaving a single kid behind]

01:29:11.500 --> 01:29:12.220
Ji-an's, Tae-seong's…

01:29:12.220 --> 01:29:12.770
[Tae-seong!
Not leaving a single kid behind]

01:29:12.770 --> 01:29:13.510
[You said earlier Ye-eun
is the vice class president, right?]

01:29:13.510 --> 01:29:14.250
[Not leaving anyone out]

01:29:14.420 --> 01:29:14.650
[Carefully prepared – all kinds
of surprises that will blow their minds]

01:29:14.650 --> 01:29:16.580
When they open the door and walk in…

01:29:16.910 --> 01:29:18.230
If it can just be like this,
that's enough.

01:29:18.230 --> 01:29:20.160
[I called the champion 000]

01:29:20.190 --> 01:29:20.500
[Industry No.1 – invited a big name]

01:29:20.500 --> 01:29:22.260
You called 000, the champion?

01:29:22.260 --> 01:29:22.580
[And the special helper
invited by Jennie × Sooji]

01:29:22.580 --> 01:29:24.570
Sis, sis! The phone's ringing!

01:29:25.890 --> 01:29:27.830
[Secret Manito – The Day]

01:29:28.120 --> 01:29:28.250
[Finally revealed]

01:29:28.250 --> 01:29:29.180
This is crazy.

01:29:29.800 --> 01:29:30.730
Yeah, this is it.

01:29:30.760 --> 01:29:30.870
This is seriously insane.

01:29:30.870 --> 01:29:31.770
[The long-awaited secret surprise]

01:29:31.770 --> 01:29:32.580
This is it.

01:29:32.690 --> 01:29:34.410
The kids are definitely
going to be so happy.

01:29:34.410 --> 01:29:35.520
[A friend appearing at that moment…!]

01:29:35.580 --> 01:29:37.030
[Friend! Friend!!!]

01:29:37.190 --> 01:29:39.770
[Unexpectedly adorable Manitos
make their entrance]

01:29:39.770 --> 01:29:41.140
Seriously. So cute.

01:29:41.140 --> 01:29:42.320
[But… more than one?]

01:29:42.320 --> 01:29:43.880
-So many came!
-There are more and more!

01:29:43.880 --> 01:29:44.990
[Elementary students flooding in!]

01:29:44.990 --> 01:29:46.220
Why are there suddenly this many?

01:29:46.220 --> 01:29:46.720
Now...

01:29:47.080 --> 01:29:48.010
Oh my gosh, this…

01:29:48.170 --> 01:29:49.370
[There are people inside!!!]

01:29:49.720 --> 01:29:51.470
[Please change it for me!
Unpredictable elementary school energy]

01:29:51.470 --> 01:29:52.570
[Out of control – Manitos in crisis]

01:29:52.570 --> 01:29:53.210
Hold on!

01:29:54.300 --> 01:29:54.520
[Can they successfully
deliver this special day?!]

01:29:54.520 --> 01:29:55.890
Oh no, oh no—this is bad.

01:29:56.370 --> 01:29:57.520
This is really not a joke.